This doesn't seem to be the case any more in 16.8.0.41105:
```
/// <summary>
///   覆寫目前執行緒的 CurrentUICulture 屬性，對象是所有
///   使用這個強類型資源類別的資源查閱。
/// </summary>
```

(I'm assuming that's right, since the two lines look different.)

I'm guessing that either it was resolved more recently (hard to imagine unless your command line MSBuild version and your VS MSBuild version are different) or you got a version from between when the string changed and when the localized versions were produced—it sometimes takes a little time to get localized strings. If it's the latter, sorry about that! Can you try updating VS to the latest version and seeing if it works?
